  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The purpose of Homes and Communities activity is to ensure that all Rwandan children have literacy-supportive, stimulating and safe home and community environments. This will be achieved through improving home literacy environments and learning opportunities for children with disabilities and increasing community engagement in promoting childrens literacy.</narrative>
